# PersonalMatch — Cursor Rules

Refer to PROJECT.md for the full architecture and phase breakdown. Follow it exactly.

## Critical Rules

- Commit after EVERY PROJECT.md step with the exact commit message
- NEVER hardcode URLs, credentials, thresholds, weights, or model names — use config/settings.py
- Scoring is deterministic; LLM only explains pre-computed scores
- Python 3.11+, type hints, Google docstrings, logging not print()
- Scripts runnable via `pip install -e .` then `python scripts/script_name.py`
- Integration tests use `@pytest.mark.integration` and `RUN_INTEGRATION=1`

See cursorrules at repo root for the full rule set.
